@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vosjbs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((0.72 + (v0 + 0.10 * v1 + 0.98)))
    v2 = 0.99
    tmp = v0
    v0 = (0.73 / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.78) / (v1 + 0.37 * v0 + 0.55)))
    tmp = v0
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
